                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d595">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">611.5231/352: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Spain</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Moore</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Madrid</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1924-04-07T17:00:00+00:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 7, 1924—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[Received April 7—5 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>16. Your cipher telegram of April 4, 5 p.m. Urgent prorogation present <hi
                        rend="italic">iwdus vivendi</hi> without modification for 6 months or year
                    seems utmost that can be accomplished under existing circumstances. Since I am
                    to see General Primo de Rivera very soon, please cable soonest possible whether
                    I may accept for our Government such a solution if proffered.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Moore</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
